{"tid":286061,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"(有圖) 求Michael Fassbender 電影","createTime":"2017-06-16T10:05:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-16T10:08:19.000Z","uid":18863,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"753666530b5a73367e01db51af1c6b89099e8b5a","tid":286061,"uid":18863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T10:05:07.000Z","msg":"我前幾日上網見到有一條大陸廣告 用咗一套電影嘅節錄但改咗啲字幕嘅廣告<br />\n我見到Michael Fassbender同埋Marion Cotillard<br />\n咁我google佢地一齊拍過嘅電影 但我搵到得Assassin's Creed同埋Macbeth<br />\n兩套都好似比較中古時期啲 但我見到個套片喺好現代的<br />\n咁我去Michael Fassbender IMDB搵到一張劇照 但偏偏冇個電影名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想上嚟問下全能的連登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個對白類似喺咁的：<br />\nMarion Cotillard :If you allow me, I can teach you how to control it.<br />\nMichael Fassbender : What is it... the machine<br />\nMarion Cotillard : It is genetic memory...乜乜乜乜<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n劇照在此：<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/16/180040_5e10a57d8bcfedb9f1ecdfa9f350f0a6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F16%2F180040_5e10a57d8bcfedb9f1ecdfa9f350f0a6.jpg&h=a20db7bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔該晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdc9cd0417f8ad65d80e98bb54ec5f165e278b59","tid":286061,"uid":71712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T10:06:15.000Z","msg":"assassin creed 黎"},{"pid":"1f4bb3ee6db1851e7358ad768d3cbb2817817e86","tid":286061,"uid":8496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T10:07:03.000Z","msg":"咁既對白，我第一時間諗起Assassin's Creed<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68177689eb96092da8aec9589ff6fc8d45e3f4d1","tid":286061,"uid":81397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T10:07:18.000Z","msg":"Ac"},{"pid":"d8d4a7d12a93475b520550336e26ec40f3cb11e0","tid":286061,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T10:07:59.000Z","msg":"你咪自己答左<br />\nAC"},{"pid":"70db3539968a85bce413ee52ae11ad81a6e7fe91","tid":286061,"uid":18863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T10:08:19.000Z","msg":"唔該晒大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我以為AC喺啲中古電影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n麻煩晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}